scene.message:
Nanjo: Every last one of you.{nl}
A foolish curse is nothing{nl}
but superstition.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: A secret shortcut...{nl}
Oh, you mean that hole that{nl}
opened up in the wall?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Passing by the SEBEC{nl}
building at night is the one{nl}
thing I can't stand.{waitkey}They tore down a haunted{nl}
house, so that company's{nl}
cursed!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: I'm starving, gonna{nl}
go grab a bite...{wait_fr:32} The secret{nl}
shortcut's faster, sir! I{nl}
recommend it, sir!{waitkey}{ret}
